abstract: Tiger Woods responds to injury reports by posting video on Twitter of himself swinging golf club.

headline.main: Tiger Woods Posts Video of Swing

snippet: Tiger Woods posted a video of himself swinging a golf club in an effort to rebut recent reports that suggested he had endured setbacks in his recovery from back operations.
lead_paragraph: Tiger Woods posted a video of himself swinging a golf club in an effort to rebut recent reports that suggested he had endured setbacks in his recovery from back operations.
